	Let $H \in \Obj(\Hilb)$ and $E \subset H$ a closed subspace of $H$. Then $E^{\perp} \oplus E$ something about $E^{\perp} \cong H/E$ and adding up to $H$. \tcr{FINISH!!!}
\end{ex}

